section.title: Source Comments
section.text:
AMITA Health is the largest Catholic health system based in Illinois. We offer more than 150 locations around the state, in communities large and small, so health care access is convenient. With 19 Catholic and Adventist hospitals, over 25 long-term care and senior living facilities, dozens of physician offices and health centers, home care, hospice, behavioral health services and more.
Currently six of our Hospitals are live on the Epic system, they are:
**** AMITA Health Resurrection Medical Center - Chicago
**** AMITA Health Saint Francis Hospital - Evanston
**** AMITA Health Saint Joseph Hospital - Chicago
**** AMITA Health Saint Mary of Nazareth Hospital - Chicago
**** AMITA Health Saint Elizabeth Hospital - Chicago
**** AMITA Health Holy Family Medical Center - Des PlainesAscension Illinois
